    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被允许的技术只有反击，用格挡拯救世界!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在硬核动作游戏《Parryman》中考验你的招架技巧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >格挡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《格挡侠》 是一款只能使用招架来前进的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >格挡是一种难度较高的技能，但可以用来一击解决大多数敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些陷阱也可以招架，让你在后坐力的作用下做出各种动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.poster.avif?t=1742542336\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.webm?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/5ff9435e51d383796a6274a127528eb1.mp4?t=1742542336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个拥有强大科学技术的群体。岛上的居民已经屈服并与你作对，你需要用 “格挡 ”来对付他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264400/extras_big/0dab1916ae9607dd4e3e1c24f0856074.avif?t=1742542336 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
